title: Notice Was Returned To USCIS Because The Post Office Could Not Deliver It
body: On May 18, 2021, the Post Office returned a notice we sent you for your Form I-751, Petition to Remove Conditions on Residence, Receipt Number YSC2190136000, because they could not deliver it. This could have a serious effect on your case. Please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice immediately. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Expedite Request Denied
body: On May 17, 2021, we denied your request for expedited processing of your I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190136530. We review all expedite requests on a case-by-case basis, and we grant them at the discretion of the director. Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
